OL,3,CThree taken to hospital after tumble
OL,4,Cdryer fire
OL,6,FPeople are being warned about the
OL,7,Fdangers of trying to tackle fires
OL,8,Fthemselves after a tumble dryer caught
OL,9,Falight in the basement of a Jersey
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FThree residents were taken to the
OL,13,FGeneral Hospital by paramedics for
OL,14,Fpossible smoke inhalation following
OL,15,Fthe incident, which was reported in St
OL,16,FHelier just after 6pm on Tuesday (16
OL,17,FJune).
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
