CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781722095
OL,3,CThree taken to hospital after tumble
OL,4,Cdryer fire
OL,6,FJersey Fire and Rescue say the
OL,7,Foccupants had evacuated the property
OL,8,Fby the time they arrived, but one had
OL,9,Finitially tried to fight the flames.
OL,11,FWatch Commander Ryan says: "I would
OL,12,Fstrongly discourage members of the
OL,13,Fpublic from attempting to tackle fires
OL,14,Fthemselves.
OL,16,F"Fires can develop rapidly, and smoke
OL,17,Fcan become life-threatening within
OL,18,Fminutes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
