FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781722095
OL,3,CThree taken to hospital after tumble
OL,4,Cdryer fire
OL,6,F"If a fire occurs, leave the property
OL,7,Fimmediately, ensure everyone is
OL,8,Faccounted for, close doors where
OL,9,Fpossible on your way out to help
OL,10,Fcontain the fire, and call the
OL,11,Femergency services."
OL,13,FFirefighters wearing breathing
OL,14,Fequipment put out the blaze and then
OL,15,Fcleared the smoke through ventilation,
OL,16,Fwhich had spread to the neighbouring
OL,17,Fproperty upstairs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
